By: Herman Banken
Description:
	Upload files selected from the local filesystem 
	and upload them as raw binary to the webserver.
	
Usage:
	I recommend using this plugin together with my 
	jquery-dropzone plugin. This plugin will convert 
	all matched nodes to DropZone's and when connected 
	to this upload plugin this makes a very powerfull 
	and user friendly tool for your admin users.
